{"tid":2002874,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺華晨宇係當今最強創作歌手,繼周杰倫後第二個天才  ?","createTime":"2020-05-05T12:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T08:52:23.000Z","uid":353419,"like":6,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"756d9bf86be0a3633c2cec6c4dbdccf7dcf583fa","tid":2002874,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"李榮浩方大同的歌都好聽，美中不足係太似John Mayer，冇周杰倫咁開創有別於外國的R&amp;B<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i97JVa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi97JVa0.jpg&h=d9508d03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華晨宇的歌有突破性，創新的風格，而唔係模仿外國，就好似當年的周杰倫咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a03AMfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa03AMfS.jpg&h=a8f09568&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林夕話張國榮係顏色不一樣的煙火，而華晨宇就係煙火裡的塵埃，所以就填左首歌比佢，呼應番張國榮的＂我＂，算係意志的傳承。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ji8-2f0B1Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4ji8-2f0B1Y&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=01fe77b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ji8-2f0B1Y</a><br />\n<br />\n七重人格，一首歌入面七個演繹方法，痴撚線。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rKat2yksyHM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrKat2yksyHM&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=f4ffd497\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rKat2yksyHM</a><br />\n<br />\n華晨宇曲風獨特創新，首首都唔同Feel，好似依首講癌症的絕望感，成首歌一個字都冇，靜係得呼喊聲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BEx8Nfu2VsQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBEx8Nfu2VsQ&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=050ea560\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BEx8Nfu2VsQ</a><br />\n<br />\n啲人成日覺得佢只識鳩叫，但佢依首抒情歌都好正，唱法又有別於大路Ｋ歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WCjC_f1A5SQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWCjC_f1A5SQ&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=1a9e0058\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WCjC_f1A5SQ</a><br />\n唔係話佢係第二個周杰倫，神台級冇得比，純粹覺得佢係繼周杰倫後，第二個人將新元素帶比華語樂壇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RPWDeLqsN0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRPWDeLqsN0g&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=455b1829\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RPWDeLqsN0g</a><br />\n<br />\n純屬主觀睇法，我的睇法未必岩，希望同大家交流討論下"},{"pid":"fcf1fe2113b08d499a4d0d24ea99034c8b4ea100","tid":2002874,"uid":203955,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：中國人有創意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8dd5881e9f51407ec27fa9fad1af190f2b2077","tid":2002874,"uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"fcf1fe2113b08d499a4d0d24ea99034c8b4ea100","tid":2002874,"uid":203955,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：中國人有創意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"我純粹從音樂上去睇，<br />\n依首歌入面有七個唱腔，代表七種性格，<br />\n童真，殘忍，理性，控制欲，浪漫，悲觀，癲狂<br />\n我覺得好有創意，唱同埋作都難度極高<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nkOBO62BJ4E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnkOBO62BJ4E&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=6c3648d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nkOBO62BJ4E</a>"},{"pid":"b49c039aaa0ac767bd9b16a08c878e2fbc3f8cb0","tid":2002874,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"係陶傑開創"},{"pid":"4ed4103b9b2aecaf67dbd7ab6f61ec57e4f7f39a","tid":2002874,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:40:56.000Z","msg"